{
  "texts": [
    "Data preprocessing and data normalization, eliminating redundant information and unreasonable data; 3.",
    "Feature engineering: Feature construction is carried out by pairing sgRNA sequence information with target sequence bases; 4.",
    "Feature selection, using feature selection algorithm to select features related to the target; 5.",
    "Train the model, calculate the evaluation scores of the training set and the verification set by cross-validation method to judge the model fitting and optimize the model parameter index; 6.",
    "Model evaluation: error analysis was carried out through relevant independent data to evaluate the accuracy and generalization ability of the model (Liu et al2020)."
